high_descs: Turn right and walk to the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Turn left and walk to the sink on the right.
Slice the tomato in the back.
Turn left, then left, then left again to face the stove.
Place the knife on the counter to the left.
Turn left to face the sink.
Take a slice of tomato from the sink.
Turn right and walk to the stove.
Open the microwave door above the stove, place the slice inside, close the door, and turn the microwave on. remove it when it's done and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the counter on the left.
Put the slice on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a microwaved tomato slice on the counter.

high_descs: Turn right and walks past the stove, to the counter top where the coffee pot is.
Pick up the knife on the corner of the counter, to the right of the coffee pot.
Turn to your left and walk to the sink.
Cut the tomato closest to the back of the sink into slices.
Turn around so that you are facing the stove.
Set the knife on the green counter top, in front of the spatula.
Turn back around so that you are facing the sink again.
Pick up one of the slices of tomato previously cut.
Turn to your right and walk straight until you reach the stove.
Place the tomato slice in the microwave, turn the microwave on and wait a moment, then close the microwave door.
Turn around and walk straight until you reach the middle of the kitchen island
Place the tomato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated tomato slice on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and approach the coffee maker.
Pick up the knife from the counter.
Turn left and go to the sink.
Slice the tomato in the sink.
Turn to the right
Put the knife on the counter to the right of the sink.
Turn back to the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato.
Turn right and go to the microwave.
Heat the slice of tomato in the microwave.
Turn right and go to the table.
Put the tomato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a warmed slice of tomato on the table.

high_descs: Go to the right to the counter where the coffee pot is.
Pick up the butter knife that is on the counter.
Go to the left to the sink.
Use the knife to slice the tomato closest to the faucet.
Go to the counter directly to the right of the sink.
Put the butter knife down on the counter.
Go back to the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato out of the sink.
Turn to the right and go forward to the microwave.
Put the tomato inside the microwave and turn it on to cook, then remove the tomato from the microwave.
Turn around and go to the green table across from the sink.
Put the tomato on the table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cooked tomato on the table.

high_descs: Turn right and walk forward to face the counter.
Pick up the knife on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the sink.
Cut the top tomato in the sink into slices.
Take a step to the right to face the counter.
Put the knife on the counter.
Take a step to the left to face the sink.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the sink.
Turn to the right and walk forward to face the microwave.
Heat the tomato slice in the microwave and then remove it.
Turn around and walk forward and then turn left to face the table in the center of the room.
Place the tomato slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: To cut a slice of tomato plus set it on the counter.
